                        <interp inst="t18460706-name-202" type="given" value="ELIZA"></interp>ELIZA CROOKS</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> My bed-room door was closed—my husband went to bed last.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18460706-name-203" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18460706-name-203" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460706-name-203" type="surname" value="CROOKS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460706-name-203" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE CROOKS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the husband of the last witness—I went to bed about half-past twelve o'clock—I am sure I shut the bed-room door.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I saw a man drop the things in the street and walk away.</p>
